{"word":"G4450 - πυῤῥός - pyrrhós - poor-hros' - Red","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πυῤῥός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pyrrhós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">poor-hros'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Red</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சிவப்பான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"having the color of fire, red"},{"paragraph":"பெரோயா ஊரான் - PyrThus ஒருவருடைய பெயர்"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4442 - πῦρ - pŷr - poor/4442\">G4442</a>; <i>fire like</i>, that is, (specifically) <i>flame colored:</i> - red.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4442/4442\">G4442</a>, <a href=\"#/G4443/4443\">G4443</a>, <a href=\"#/G4447/4447\">G4447</a>, <a href=\"#/G4448/4448\">G4448</a>, <a href=\"#/G4449/4449\">G4449</a>, <a href=\"#/G4450/4450\">G4450</a>, <a href=\"#/G4451/4451\">G4451</a>"}]}